<!-- About -->
<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
        <h2>Portland Chinese Christian &amp; Missionary Alliance</h2>
        <p>As a multicultural church, we have services in English, Cantonese, and Mandarin. We believe in serving the local community by organizing events such as VBS and Saturday Chinese school. We believe in reviving the city by preaching the Gospel and sharing God's love.</p>
      </div>
